{"tid":335384,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)你的名字 世紀末光煞 時凶獵殺","createTime":"2017-07-25T13:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T18:52:56.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f98f0434249ee6b4210369e48b83eb5f5e788002","tid":335384,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=k3VEgyUZAXQ3epH%2FW0uw1whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=89c4468a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK或者加V台個網入白名單好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=k3VEgyUZAXQ3epH%2FW0uw1whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1ffb0b13\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=k3VEgyUZAXQ3epH%2FW0uw1whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=72c0108e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4e/Your_name_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4e%2FYour_name_poster.jpg&h=91b3734e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Darkest_Hour_Theatrical_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Darkest_Hour_Theatrical_Poster.jpg&h=e8c68076&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/looper/assets/images/onesheet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonypictures.com%2Fmovies%2Flooper%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fonesheet.jpg&h=a9cc8c48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.迪亞馬特彗星（ティアマト彗星）每逢1200年造訪地球，在深山小鎮糸守町（糸守町／いともりまち）[註 7]中家族世代經營鎮內「宮水神社」的高中少女宮水三葉、以及東京四谷[註 8]的高中少年立花瀧，從某天開始，在睡覺的時候，就會靈魂互換，醒來什麼都不記得，感覺像做了奇妙的夢，但周圍的人會講出他們昨天有違平常。他倆很快意識到這種情形，困惑之中開始在彼此智慧型手機留言，逐漸地變得習慣於身體切換，並干預對方的生活。三葉不僅樂於所嚮往的東京生活，也利用女人心這點..<br />\n<br />\n2.講述一群年青的美國遊客在莫斯科旅遊時，遭遇外星物種入侵，奮力抵抗、掙扎求生的故事..<br />\n<br />\n3.在近未來的世界，21世紀70年代，時空旅行的技術被開發了出來。這項技術被嚴格控制，只有黑社會非法使用。由於在70年代個人身份識別技術的發展，處理屍體非常困難，黑社會於是將想要殺的人蒙面、捆綁，再藉由時空旅行傳送回三十年前，由21世紀40年代的黑幫組織負責殺害、焚屍滅跡..<br />\n<br />\n10 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad74de6957a427290eebcd967943b53ec70c274","tid":335384,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e573ed09b63e43ef476a8993c86a4f8cea85b98","tid":335384,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6d89448747d294c965096fbfc710fe942242b1","tid":335384,"uid":27362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"你的名字 1080？"},{"pid":"a2d5c14a138be5cf1